<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>GUNDAM SEED • 机动战士档案馆</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/3.12.5/gsap.min.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <!-- Google Fonts loaded via <link> with crossorigin for valid CORS handling (avoids font loading blocks) -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&family=Playfair+Display:wght@700&display=swap">
    <style>
        :root {
            --seed-red: #C8102E;
            --seed-blue: #0033A0;
            --seed-gold: #C5A26E;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;
            background: #0A0A0A;
            color: #EDE6D8;
            font-feature-settings: "kern" "liga" "tnum";
        }

        .heading {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: -0.04em;
            line-height: 1.05;
        }

        /* Immersive Cinematic Typography Scale */
        .cinematic-title {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: -0.05em;
            line-height: 0.95;
        }

        .gundam-card {
            transition: all 0.55s cubic-bezier(0.23, 1, 0.32, 1);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
            background: #0A0A0A;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px -4px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.5);
        }
        
        .gundam-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px) scale(1.01);
            box-shadow: 0 40px 90px -20px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.7), 
                        0 0 0 1px rgba(197, 162, 110, 0.2);
            border-color: #C5A26E;
        }
        
        /* Extreme cinematic film strip treatment (A) */
        .gundam-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            border: 10px solid #0A0A0A;
            box-shadow: inset 0 0 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 2;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        /* Film perforations - left side only for reel authenticity */
        .gundam-card::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            left: 6px;
            top: 10px;
            bottom: 10px;
            width: 7px;
            background: repeating-linear-gradient(
                #111 0px,
                #111 7px,
                transparent 7px,
                transparent 20px
            );
            z-index: 5;
            pointer-events: none;
            opacity: 0.75;
            box-shadow: 1px 0 0 #222;
        }
        
        .gundam-card:hover::before {
            opacity: 0.65;
        }
        
        /* Projector light leak on hover */
        .gundam-card:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 50px 120px -25px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.75),
                        0 0 0 1px rgba(197,162,110,0.25),
                        0 0 40px rgba(197,162,110,0.15);
        }
        
        .gundam-card .NEW-badge {
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }
        .gundam-card:hover .NEW-badge {
            transform: scale(1.08);
        }

        .gundam-card::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, rgba(0,0,0,0.7));
            opacity: 0.6;
            transition: opacity 0.3s;
        }

        .character-card {
            transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.23, 1, 0.32, 1);
            will-change: transform, box-shadow;
            transform: translateZ(0);
        }

        .character-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px) translateZ(0);
            border-color: #C5A26E;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px -8px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.4);
        }

        /* Stronger premium touch feedback on main character cards (mobile + desktop delight) */
        .character-card:active {
            transform: scale(0.955) translateZ(0);
            transition-duration: 55ms;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(197,162,110,0.35), 0 10px 18px -4px rgba(0,0,0,0.35);
        }

        .section-label {
            font-size: 10px;
            letter-spacing: 4px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #C5A26E;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }

        .ms-image {
            transition: transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.23, 1, 0.32, 1);
            image-rendering: -webkit-optimize-contrast;
            image-rendering: crisp-edges;
            filter: contrast(1.12) saturate(1.15);
        }
        
        .gundam-card:hover .ms-image {
            transform: scale(1.08);
        }

        /* 全局极致画质提升 */
        img {
            image-rendering: -webkit-optimize-contrast;
            image-rendering: crisp-edges;
            filter: contrast(1.08) saturate(1.12);
            transition: filter 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        img:hover {
            filter: contrast(1.15) saturate(1.2);
        }

        .character-card img,
        .group img {
            filter: contrast(1.1) saturate(1.15) brightness(1.02);
        }

        /* Uniform image frame treatment for ALL main character cards (real images + placeholders) */
        .character-card .char-portrait-frame {
            transition: transform 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.23,1,0.32,1), border-color 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }
        .character-card:hover .char-portrait-frame {
            transform: scale(1.03);
            border-color: #C5A26E;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(197,162,110,0.12) inset;
        }

        /* Strict unified picture sizing & framing for main characters grid */
        .character-card .char-portrait-frame img {
            object-fit: cover !important;
            object-position: center 18% !important;
            width: 100% !important;
            height: 100% !important;
            display: block;
            filter: contrast(1.08) saturate(1.12) brightness(1.01);
        }
        .character-card .char-portrait-frame > div.archive-ember {
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        .nav-link {
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .nav-link:after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            width: 0;
            height: 1px;
            bottom: -2px;
            left: 0;
            background-color: #C5A26E;
            transition: width 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .nav-link:hover:after {
            width: 100%;
        }

        .modal {
            animation: modalEnter 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.23, 1, 0.32, 1) forwards;
        }
        
        @keyframes modalEnter {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        #seed-entrance {
            transition: opacity 1.2s ease;
        }

        /* ==================== FAVORITES SYSTEM - Premium Personal Archive ==================== */
        .fav-heart {
            position: absolute;
            top: 14px;
            left: 14px;
            z-index: 20;
            width: 32px;
            height: 32px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.65);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
            border-radius: 9999px;
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 15px;
            transition: all 0.2s cubic-bezier(0.23, 1, 0.32, 1);
            cursor: pointer;
            backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
            will-change: transform, background, border-color;
        }
        .fav-heart:hover {
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.85);
            border-color: #C5A26E;
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }
        .fav-heart.active {
            color: #C8102E;
            background: rgba(198, 162, 110, 0.15);
            border-color: #C5A26E;
        }
        .fav-heart.active i {
            animation: favPop 0.35s cubic-bezier(0.23,1,0.32,1);
        }
        @keyframes favPop {
            0% { transform: scale(0.6); }
            50% { transform: scale(1.35); }
            100% { transform: scale(1); }
        }

        /* Mobile-optimized filter bar */
        #gundam-filters {
            scrollbar-width: none;
            -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
            display: none; /* Temporarily hidden for immersive reel redesign */
        }
        #gundam-filters-wrapper {
            display: none; /* Hiding old heavy filters during cinematic redesign */
        }
        .filter-chip {
            flex-shrink: 0;
            transition: all 0.2s cubic-bezier(0.23, 1, 0.32, 1);
        }
        .filter-chip.active {
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(197, 162, 110, 0.4);
        }
        .filter-chip:active {
            transform: scale(0.96);
        }

        /* === Female Fate Dance Modal - Cinematic Premium === */
        .dance-modal {
            animation: danceModalEnter 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.23, 1, 0.32, 1) forwards;
        }
        @keyframes danceModalEnter {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.96) translateY(30px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1) translateY(0); }
        }
        .dance-video-container {
            position: relative;
            background: #000;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .dance-video-container::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 30%, transparent 40%, rgba(0,0,0,0.4) 75%);
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 2;
            mix-blend-mode: multiply;
        }
        .film-grain-overlay {
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background-image: 
                linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.035) 1px, transparent 1px),
                linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.025) 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 3px 3px;
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 3;
            opacity: 0.6;
            mix-blend-mode: screen;
        }

        /* Music-reactive Nolan vignette pulse for dance archive (cinematic poetry) */
        .dance-video-container.music-pulse {
            animation: danceMusicBreath 2.8s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        .dance-video-container.music-pulse.lacus { animation-duration: 3.6s; box-shadow: inset 0 0 90px rgba(180,160,120,0.12); }
        .dance-video-container.music-pulse.lunamaria { animation-duration: 2.1s; box-shadow: inset 0 0 90px rgba(200,90,90,0.14); }
        .dance-video-container.music-pulse.cagalli { animation-duration: 1.65s; box-shadow: inset 0 0 90px rgba(190,130,80,0.16); }
        .dance-video-container.music-pulse.natarle { animation-duration: 2.9s; box-shadow: inset 0 0 80px rgba(150,160,180,0.12); }
        .dance-video-container.music-pulse.meyrin { animation-duration: 3.2s; box-shadow: inset 0 0 85px rgba(140,170,150,0.11); }

        @keyframes danceMusicBreath {
            0%, 100% { box-shadow: inset 0 0 80px rgba(197,162,110,0.06); }
            50% { box-shadow: inset 0 0 140px rgba(197,162,110,0.18); }
        }

        /* One-time Nolan "declassified" stamp on dance video start (delightful archive detail) */
        .dance-video-container .declassified-stamp {
            position: absolute;
            top: 22%;
            right: 12%;
            transform: rotate(12deg);
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
            font-size: 11px;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            color: #C5A26E;
            opacity: 0;
            border: 1px solid #C5A26E;
            padding: 2px 11px;
            z-index: 10;
            pointer-events: none;
            text-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
        }

        /* Delightful Nolan film reel micro-interaction on random note button */
        .cinematic-film-button:active i {
            transform: rotate(180deg);
            transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.23,1,0.32,1);
        }
        .cinematic-film-button:hover i {
            color: #C5A26E;
        }

        /* Favorites count badge - cinematic classified feel */
        .fav-count {
            font-size: 9px;
            padding: 1px 6px;
            background: #C5A26E;
            color: black;
            border-radius: 999px;
            margin-left: 4px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }

        /* Accessibility & Focus Polish (cinematic but usable) */
        .gundam-card:focus-visible,
        .gundam-card:focus {
            outline: 2px solid #C5A26E;
            outline-offset: 3px;
        }
        button:focus-visible,
        .nav-link:focus-visible,
        input:focus-visible {
            outline: 2px solid #C5A26E;
            outline-offset: 2px;
        }
        .fav-heart:focus-visible {
            outline: 2px solid #C5A26E;
            outline-offset: 1px;
        }

        /* ==================== NOLAN CINEMATIC PREMIUM POLISH - Background Optimization Pass ==================== */
        
        /* Deep film grain + vignette for living archive authenticity (Nolan 35mm feel) */
        body::before {
            content: '';
            position: fixed;
            inset: 0;
            background-image: 
                linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.045) 50%, transparent 50%),
                linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0,0,0,0.032) 50%, transparent 50%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 50% 30%, rgba(197,162,110,0.012) 0%, transparent 65%);
            background-size: 3px 3px, 4px 4px, 120% 120%;
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 1;
            mix-blend-mode: multiply;
            opacity: 0.72;
        }

        /* Subtle global cinematic letterbox feel on large screens */
        @media (min-width: 1280px) {
            body::after {
                content: '';
                position: fixed;
                inset: 0;
                background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent 8%, rgba(0,0,0,0.06) 12%, transparent 88%, rgba(0,0,0,0.05) 92%);
                pointer-events: none;
                z-index: 2;
            }
        }

        /* Enhanced Gundam card - Nolan tension & premium living archive delight */
        .gundam-card {
            transition: transform 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.23, 1, 0.32, 1), 
                        box-shadow 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.23, 1, 0.32, 1),
                        border-color 0.4s ease;
            will-change: transform, box-shadow;
            backface-visibility: hidden;
            transform: translateZ(0);
        }
        
        .gundam-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-11px) scale(1.006) translateZ(0);
            box-shadow: 0 35px 80px -18px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.65), 
                        0 0 0 1px rgba(197, 162, 110, 0.15) inset;
            border-color: #C5A26E;
        }
        
        /* Cinematic light sweep on card image (fate spotlight) */
        .gundam-card .h-80::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(
                125deg,
                transparent 20%,
                rgba(255,255,255,0.08) 46%,
                rgba(197,162,110,0.25) 51%,
                rgba(255,255,255,0.08) 56%,
                transparent 80%
            );
            background-size: 280% 100%;
            background-position: 280% 0;
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.4s ease, background-position 1.1s cubic-bezier(0.23,1,0.32,1);
            z-index: 3;
            pointer-events: none;
            mix-blend-mode: screen;
        }
        
        .gundam-card:hover .h-80::before {
            opacity: 1;
            background-position: -160% 0;
        }
        
        /* Subtle film grain on the suit projection */
        .gundam-card .h-80::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background-image: 
                linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.025) 1px, transparent 1px),
                linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 3px 3px;
            opacity: 0.5;
            mix-blend-mode: overlay;
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 2;
            transition: opacity 0.6s;
        }
        .gundam-card:hover .h-80::after {
            opacity: 0.75;
        }

        /* === NEW: Character Archive Reveal (for the 6 freshly declassified portraits) === */
        .character-card img {
            transition: filter 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.23,1,0.32,1), transform 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.23,1,0.32,1);
        }
        .character-card:hover img {
            filter: contrast(1.18) saturate(1.22) brightness(1.03);
            transform: scale(1.035);
        }
        /* Subtle Nolan film-ember + declassified stamp pulse on real portrait cards */
        .character-card .archive-ember {
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 35% 25%, rgba(197,162,110,0.18) 0%, transparent 55%);
            opacity: 0;
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 3;
            mix-blend-mode: screen;
            transition: opacity 1.1s ease;
        }
        .character-card:hover .archive-ember {
            opacity: 0.65;
        }
        @keyframes archiveDeclassify {
            0% { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(4px) scale(0.985); }
            35% { opacity: 0.9; }
            100% { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(0) scale(1); }
        }
        .character-card.revealed .archive-ember {
            animation: archiveDeclassify 1.4s cubic-bezier(0.23,1,0.32,1) forwards;
        }

        /* New declassified entry cinematic treatment (living archive poetry) */
        .character-card.new-declassified,
        .gundam-card.new-declassified {
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(197,162,110,0.25);
        }

        /* Breathing NEW badge for freshly declassified Gundams */
        .gundam-card .new-badge {
            animation: newBadgeBreath 2.2s ease-in-out infinite;
            will-change: transform;
        }
        @keyframes newBadgeBreath {
            0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); }
            50% { transform: scale(1.08); }
        }

        /* Character-tuned subtle glow on Fate Symphony label (visual music sync) */
        .dance-music-label[data-char="lacus"] { text-shadow: 0 0 6px rgba(197,162,110,0.3); }
        .dance-music-label[data-char="lunamaria"] { text-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(200,80,80,0.35); }
        .dance-music-label[data-char="cagalli"] { text-shadow: 0 0 7px rgba(180,120,60,0.4); }
        .dance-music-label[data-char="natarle"] { text-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(140,150,170,0.3); }
        .dance-music-label[data-char="meyrin"] { text-shadow: 0 0 6px rgba(160,190,160,0.3); }

        /* Synchronized subtle breathing on music label (delightful detail) */
        .dance-modal .dance-music-label {
            transition: transform 0.2s ease, opacity 0.2s ease;
        }
        @keyframes musicLabelBreath {
            0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.95; }
            50% { transform: scale(1.015); opacity: 1; }
        }

        /* Refined fate teaser for more poetic "director note" presence */
        #fate-teaser {
            transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.23, 1, 0.32, 1);
            position: relative;
        }
        #fate-teaser:hover {
            border-color: #C5A26E;
            background: rgba(197,162,110,0.06);
            color: #C5A26E;
            transform: translateY(-1px);
        }

        /* Timeline - Nolan fate folds: more alive & interactive smoothness */
        #cosmic-timeline .relative {
            transition: all 0.35s cubic-bezier(0.23, 1, 0.32, 1);
        }
        #cosmic-timeline .relative:hover {
            transform: translateX(3px);
        }
        #cosmic-timeline .relative:hover .text-2xl {
            color: #C5A26E;
        }

        /* Performance & Mobile polish */
        .gundam-card img,
        .ms-image {
            will-change: transform;
            transform: translateZ(0);
        }

        /* Filter chips - tactile premium mobile experience */
        .filter-chip {
            transition: all 0.2s cubic-bezier(0.23, 1, 0.32, 1);
            -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;
        }
        .filter-chip:active {
            transform: scale(0.97);
        }

        /* Modal cinematic upgrades */
        .fixed.inset-0 {
            animation: cinematicModalEnter 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1);
        }
        
        @keyframes cinematicModalEnter {
            from { opacity: 0; }
            to { opacity: 1; }
        }

        /* Premium mobile modal breathing room */
        @media (max-width: 640px) {
            .fixed.inset-0 > div {
                margin: 12px;
                max-height: calc(100vh - 24px);
                overflow: auto;
                -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
            }
            .fixed.inset-0 > div .p-10,
            .fixed.inset-0 > div .p-9,
            .fixed.inset-0 > div .p-8 {
                padding: 1.75rem !important;
            }
        }
        
        /* Poetic micro-detail: subtle fate pulse on key interactive elements */
        .section-label {
            position: relative;
        }
        .section-label::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -2px;
            left: 0;
            width: 0;
            height: 1px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #C5A26E, transparent);
            transition: width 1.2s ease;
        }
        .section-label:hover::after {
            width: 100%;
        }

        /* Better mobile touch targets & scroll smoothness */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .gundam-card {
                transition-duration: 0.35s;
            }
            .gundam-card:hover {
                transform: translateY(-4px) scale(1.003);
            }
            .filter-chip {
                padding-top: 0.55rem;
                padding-bottom: 0.55rem;
            }
        }

        /* Nolan cinematic timeline - subtle time ripple / visual poetry */
        #cosmic-timeline .relative {
            transition: all 0.45s cubic-bezier(0.23, 1, 0.32, 1);
            border-radius: 6px;
        }
        #cosmic-timeline .relative:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(197,162,110,0.035), transparent);
            transform: translateX(3px);
        }
        #cosmic-timeline .relative:hover .text-2xl {
            color: #C5A26E;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        }

        /* Timeline click "time fold" cinematic feedback */
        #cosmic-timeline .relative.time-fold {
            animation: timeFold 0.9s cubic-bezier(0.23,1,0.32,1);
        }
        @keyframes timeFold {
            0% { transform: scale(1) translateX(0); filter: brightness(1); }
            40% { transform: scale(0.985) translateX(2px); filter: brightness(0.92); }
            100% { transform: scale(1) translateX(0); filter: brightness(1); }
        }

        /* Enhanced timeline item for better fate resonance */
        #cosmic-timeline .relative {
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        #cosmic-timeline .relative .fate-link {
            font-size: 10px;
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
        }
        #cosmic-timeline .relative:hover .fate-link {
            opacity: 0.6;
        }

        /* Cinematic depth on Gundam cards: focus the title, gently recede the body text on hover (Nolan close-up) */
        .gundam-card .p-6 .text-sm.text-white\/60 {
            transition: opacity 0.4s ease, transform 0.4s ease;
        }
        .gundam-card:hover .p-6 .text-sm.text-white\/60 {
            opacity: 0.55;
            transform: translateY(1px);
        }

        /* Poetic fate thread detail (living archive micro-beauty) - Nolan fate echo */
        .fate-thread {
            transition: width 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.23,1,0.32,1), opacity 0.5s ease;
            animation: fateThreadPulse 2.8s ease-in-out infinite;
            will-change: opacity;
        }
        @keyframes fateThreadPulse {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 0.32; }
            50% { opacity: 0.78; }
        }

        /* Living archive subtle breath on the entire experience (ultra low cost) */
        .max-w-7xl {
            transition: filter 12s ease;
        }
        body:hover .max-w-7xl {
            /* very gentle collective cinematic lift when engaged */
            filter: contrast(1.005) saturate(1.008);
        }

        /* Cinematic Film Reel - Horizontal scrolling strip (B + D mobile polish) */
        #gundam-grid {
            display: flex !important;
            flex-wrap: nowrap;
            overflow-x: auto;
            scroll-snap-type: x mandatory;
            gap: 1.5rem;
            padding: 1rem 0.5rem 2.5rem;
            -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
            scrollbar-width: none;
            animation: archiveBreath 22s ease-in-out infinite;
            will-change: filter;
            touch-action: pan-x;
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        /* Physical film strip aesthetic - sprocket holes on top and bottom */
        #gundam-grid::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -6px;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 6px;
            background: repeating-linear-gradient(
                90deg,
                #111 0px,
                #111 8px,
                transparent 8px,
                transparent 22px
            );
            z-index: 10;
            pointer-events: none;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }
        
        #gundam-grid::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -6px;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 6px;
            background: repeating-linear-gradient(
                90deg,
                #111 0px,
                #111 8px,
                transparent 8px,
                transparent 22px
            );
            z-index: 10;
            pointer-events: none;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }
        
        /* Current "projected" card gets stronger dramatic lighting (simulates projector beam) */
        #gundam-grid .gundam-card.current-projected {
            transform: scale(1.03) translateY(-4px);
            box-shadow: 0 60px 140px -20px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.85),
                        0 0 0 1px rgba(197,162,110,0.35),
                        0 0 60px rgba(197,162,110,0.2);
            z-index: 5;
        }
        
        /* Subtle moving film grain on the reel background - intensity reacts to Fate Profile */
        #gundam-grid .film-grain-layer {
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background-image: 
                linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.022) 1px, transparent 1px),
                linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.015) 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 3px 3px;
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 1;
            opacity: 0.65;
            animation: filmGrainMove 3.8s linear infinite;
            mix-blend-mode: screen;
        }
        
        @keyframes filmGrainMove {
            0% { background-position: 0 0; }
            100% { background-position: 3px 3px; }
        }
        #gundam-grid::-webkit-scrollbar {
            display: none;
        }
        
        #gundam-grid .gundam-card {
            flex: 0 0 300px;
            scroll-snap-align: start;
            min-height: 420px;
        }
        
        @media (min-width: 768px) {
            #gundam-grid .gundam-card {
                flex: 0 0 340px;
            }
        }
        
        @media (min-width: 1280px) {
            #gundam-grid .gundam-card {
                flex: 0 0 360px;
            }
        }
        
        @keyframes archiveBreath {
            0%, 100% { filter: brightness(1.0) contrast(1.0); }
            50% { filter: brightness(0.985) contrast(1.012); }
        }

        /* Premium Nolan "opening the classified file" vignette for random note modal */
        .random-note-vignette {
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 40%, transparent 35%, rgba(0,0,0,0.45) 78%);
            pointer-events: none;
            opacity: 0.85;
            mix-blend-mode: multiply;
        }

        /* Fate resonance glow support for cards */
        .gundam-card.fate-resonance {
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px rgba(197,162,110,0.65) !important,
                        0 0 25px rgba(197,162,110,0.25);
            transition: box-shadow 0.4s ease;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .gundam-card.fate-resonance::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            inset: -1px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(197,162,110,0.3);
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 5;
            animation: fatePulse 3s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        
        @keyframes fatePulse {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 0.4; }
            50% { opacity: 0.9; }
        }

        /* ============================================================
           SEQUENCE 01 — STEEL WILL FILM REEL (Immersive Horizontal)
           35mm physical film language + Fate resonance projection
           Scroll-snap + drag inertia ready. Per user 5H autonomous directive.
           ============================================================ */
        .film-reel {
            display: flex !important;
            flex-wrap: nowrap;
            overflow-x: auto;
            scroll-snap-type: x mandatory;
            scroll-padding: 1.75rem;
            gap: 1rem;
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem 1.25rem;
            -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
            scrollbar-width: none;
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
            will-change: scroll-position;
            touch-action: pan-x;
        }
        .film-reel::-webkit-scrollbar {
            display: none;
        }

        /* Individual film frames — fixed width, mechanical borders, authentic perforations */
        .film-reel .gundam-card {
            flex: 0 0 328px;
            min-width: 328px;
            max-width: 328px;
            scroll-snap-align: center;
            border: 11px solid #0f0f0f;
            border-radius: 2px;
            box-shadow: 
                0 12px 28px -8px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.65),
                inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.04),
                0 0 0 1px rgba(0,0,0,0.8);
            position: relative;
            transition: transform 0.18s cubic-bezier(0.23,1,0.32,1), 
                        box-shadow 0.35s ease,
                        border-color 0.3s ease;
            will-change: transform, box-shadow;
            backface-visibility: hidden;
            transform: translateZ(0);
        }

        .film-reel .gundam-card:hover {
            transform: scale(1.012) translateY(-1px) translateZ(0);
            box-shadow: 
                0 22px 44px -10px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.72),
                0 0 0 1px rgba(197,162,110,0.12);
            z-index: 12;
        }

        /* Left-side 35mm film perforations (diegetic physical detail) */
        .film-reel .gundam-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            left: -2px;
            top: 6px;
            bottom: 6px;
            width: 8px;
            background: repeating-linear-gradient(
                to bottom,
                #0a0a0a 0px, #0a0a0a 5px,
                transparent 5px, transparent 16px
            );
            z-index: 30;
            pointer-events: none;
            border-right: 1px solid #222;
            opacity: 0.92;
            box-shadow: 1px 0 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
        }

        /* Inner projector gate frame + light leak layer */
        .film-reel .gundam-card::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            inset: 3px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
            box-shadow: inset 0 0 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.35);
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 4;
            mix-blend-mode: screen;
        }

        /* Fate resonance — colored breathing projector glow (ZAFT red / Earth blue / OB gold) */
        .film-reel .gundam-card.fate-resonance {
            box-shadow: 
                0 0 0 3px var(--res-color, #c5a26e),
                0 0 32px var(--res-color, #c5a26e),
                0 12px 28px -8px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.65) !important;
            animation: reelResonanceBreath 2.8s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        .film-reel .gundam-card.fate-resonance::before {
            opacity: 1;
            box-shadow: 1px 0 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.5), 0 0 8px var(--res-color, #c5a26e);
        }

        @keyframes reelResonanceBreath {
            0%, 100% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px var(--res-color, #c5a26e), 0 0 28px var(--res-color, #c5a26e), 0 12px 28px -8px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.65); }
            50% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px var(--res-color, #c5a26e), 0 0 48px var(--res-color, #c5a26e), 0 12px 28px -8px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.65); }
        }

        /* Dominant faction color variables (synced from updateFateResonanceVisuals) */
        .film-reel .gundam-card.dominant-zaft { --res-color: #c92a2a; }
        .film-reel .gundam-card.dominant-earth { --res-color: #4a90d9; }
        .film-reel .gundam-card.dominant-ob { --res-color: #e8b923; }

        /* Frame counter HUD — diegetic projector overlay */
        #reel-frame-counter {
            position: absolute;
            top: 12px;
            right: 18px;
            z-index: 50;
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
            font-size: 10px;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            color: #C5A26E;
            background: rgba(10,10,10,0.75);
            border: 1px solid rgba(197,162,110,0.25);
            padding: 2px 9px 1px;
            border-radius: 2px;
            pointer-events: none;
            mix-blend-mode: screen;
            transition: color 0.3s ease, border-color 0.3s ease;
        }
        #reel-frame-counter.resonant {
            color: #fff;
            border-color: #C5A26E;
            text-shadow: 0 0 6px rgba(197,162,110,0.6);
        }

        /* ============================================================
           SEQUENCE 02 — CHARACTER REEL (Cycle 05 high-density polish)
           Full film language parity with Sequence 01 + character layout adaptation.
           Wider frames for portrait+text, lighter perforations, full resonance glow.
           Reuses existing reelResonanceBreath + --res-color system.
           ============================================================ */
        .film-reel #character-grid {
            gap: 0.75rem;
            padding: 0.4rem 0.75rem 1rem;
            scroll-padding: 1rem;
        }

        .film-reel .character-card {
            flex: 0 0 312px;
            min-width: 312px;
            max-width: 312px;
            scroll-snap-align: center;
            border: 8px solid #0f0f0f;
            border-radius: 3px;
            box-shadow:
                0 8px 22px -6px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.55),
                inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
            position: relative;
            transition: transform 0.18s cubic-bezier(0.23,1,0.32,1),
                        box-shadow 0.32s ease;
            will-change: transform, box-shadow;
            backface-visibility: hidden;
            transform: translateZ(0);
        }

        .film-reel .character-card:hover {
            transform: scale(1.012) translateY(-1px) translateZ(0);
            box-shadow:
                0 16px 34px -8px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.68);
            z-index: 10;
        }

        /* Adapted lighter film perforations (bottom edge — respects character portrait layout) */
        .film-reel .character-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            left: 3px;
            right: 3px;
            bottom: -1px;
            height: 5px;
            background: repeating-linear-gradient(
                to right,
                #0a0a0a 0px, #0a0a0a 3px,
                transparent 3px, transparent 10px
            );
            z-index: 20;
            pointer-events: none;
            opacity: 0.65;
        }

        /* Inner projector gate + subtle vignette for character frames */
        .film-reel .character-card::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            inset: 2px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.045);
            box-shadow: inset 0 0 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 4;
            mix-blend-mode: screen;
        }

        /* Full fate-resonance on character cards — identical color breathing system */
        .film-reel .character-card.fate-resonance {
            box-shadow:
                0 0 0 2px var(--res-color, #c5a26e),
                0 0 22px var(--res-color, #c5a26e),
                0 8px 22px -6px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.55) !important;
            animation: reelResonanceBreath 2.6s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        .film-reel .character-card.fate-resonance::before {
            opacity: 0.9;
            box-shadow: 0 0 6px var(--res-color, #c5a26e);
        }

        /* Dominant faction color variables for character reel */
        .film-reel .character-card.dominant-zaft { --res-color: #c92a2a; }
        .film-reel .character-card.dominant-earth { --res-color: #4a90d9; }
        .film-reel .character-card.dominant-ob { --res-color: #e8b923; }

        /* Subtle GPU + performance hints for the second reel */
        .film-reel .character-card,
        .film-reel #character-grid {
            will-change: transform, scroll-position;
        }

        /* Live "current projected resonant frame" projector beam (Cycle 23 extension of (a))
           Stronger scale + intense fate-colored glow for the HUD's centered resonant card.
           Complements the JS .current-projected toggle + inline boost for clean persistent effect. */
        .film-reel .character-card.current-projected {
            transform: scale(1.04) translateY(-2px) !important;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(197,162,110,0.6),
                        0 0 30px rgba(197,162,110,0.4),
                        0 20px 40px -10px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.7) !important;
            z-index: 10;
        }

        /* ==================== DEEPER MOBILE CINEMATIC & PERFORMANCE ==================== */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            /* Hero more cinematic on phones (Nolan widescreen compression) */
            .relative.h-\\[92vh\\] {
                height: 88vh !important;
            }
            
            /* Gundam cards: premium tactile press with fate tension */
            .gundam-card:active {
                transform: scale(0.985) !important;
                transition-duration: 80ms;
            }

            /* Stronger delightful touch feedback on dance gallery and growth cards */
            #gallery .group:active,
            .character-card:active,
            .gundam-card.new-declassified:active {
                transform: scale(0.955);
                box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(197,162,110,0.4);
                transition-duration: 55ms;
            }
            
            /* Timeline items larger tap zones + cinematic lift */
            #cosmic-timeline .relative {
                padding: 8px 12px;
                margin-left: -8px;
                margin-right: -8px;
            }
            
            /* Fate teaser more readable + touchable */
            #fate-teaser {
                font-size: 9.5px;
                padding-top: 3px;
                padding-bottom: 3px;
            }

            /* Mobile results count: always visible and compact */
            @media (max-width: 640px) {
                #gundam-results-count {
                    font-size: 10px;
                    margin-left: 4px;
                }
                #gundam-results-count span {
                    white-space: nowrap;
                }
                #gundam-filter-summary {
                    display: none; /* keep mobile filter bar clean */
                }
            }

            /* Extra mobile polish: fate teaser becomes more prominent on touch */
            @media (max-width: 480px) {
                #fate-teaser {
                    font-size: 9px;
                    padding: 2px 6px;
                }
                #gundam-results-count {
                    display: none; /* hide detailed count on tiniest screens to keep filter bar clean */
                }
            }
            
            /* Filter bar premium horizontal scroll with momentum */
            #gundam-filters-wrapper {
                -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
                scroll-behavior: smooth;
                scrollbar-width: none;
            }
            #gundam-filters-wrapper::-webkit-scrollbar {
                display: none;
            }
            
            /* Subtle living archive idle pulse on cards (very light, perf safe) */
            .gundam-card {
                animation: mobileArchiveBreath 18s ease-in-out infinite;
            }
            @keyframes mobileArchiveBreath {
                0%, 100% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(197,162,110,0); }
                50% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(197,162,110,0.035); }
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-[#0A0A0A] text-[#EDE6D8]">

    <!-- 强袭自由高达 封面进场动画 -->
    <div id="seed-entrance" class="fixed inset-0 z-[999] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
        <!-- Full screen cover image -->
        <img loading="eager" fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" src="assets/gundam/strike-freedom-gundam.jpg" 
             class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover" 
             alt="强袭自由高达 封面 — xAI Cosmic Archive opening">
        
        <!-- Dark cinematic overlay -->
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-black/60 via-black/40 to-black/80"></div>
        
        <!-- Center content -->
        <div class="relative z-10 text-center px-6">
            <div class="mb-8">
                <div class="text-[#C5A26E] text-sm tracking-[6px] mb-2">MOBILE SUIT GUNDAM SEED</div>
                <div class="text-7xl md:text-8xl font-black tracking-[-4px] text-white" style="font-family: 'Impact', 'Arial Black', sans-serif; text-shadow: 0 0 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.8);">
                    STRIKE FREEDOM
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Enter Button (robust) -->
            <div id="enter-archive-btn"
                 class="group inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-8 py-4 border border-white/30 hover:border-[#C5A26E] rounded-full cursor-pointer transition-all active:scale-[0.985]">
                <span class="text-lg tracking-[3px] text-white group-hover:text-[#C5A26E] transition">ENTER ARCHIVE</span>
                <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right text-xl text-[#C5A26E] group-hover:translate-x-1 transition"></i>
            </div>
            
            <div class="mt-4 text-xs text-white/50 tracking-[2px]">点击进入机动战士档案馆</div>
            <div class="mt-2 text-[10px] text-white/40">建议使用 Live Server 打开以获得最佳体验（避免 file:// 限制）</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Navigation - Cinematic Film Projector Style -->
    <nav class="sticky top-0 z-50 bg-[#0A0A0A]/98 backdrop-blur-xl border-b border-white/10">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 h-14 flex items-center justify-between">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-x-4">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-x-3">
                    <div class="w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-[#C8102E] to-[#C5A26E] flex items-center justify-center ring-1 ring-white/20">
                        <span class="text-black font-bold text-xs tracking-widest">SEED</span>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <div class="font-semibold tracking-[-0.5px] text-sm">GUNDAM SEED</div>
                        <div class="text-[9px] text-white/40 -mt-1 tracking-[1px]">COSMIC ERA • 71-73</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Fate Signature - Now more prominent -->
                <div onclick="if(window.fateProfile){const p=window.fateProfile; alert(`xAI COSMIC ARCHIVIST v4.3\n\n${p.signature}\n\nInteractions: ${p.totalInteractions}`)}" 
                     class="hidden md:flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-white/10 hover:border-[#C5A26E]/60 cursor-pointer transition group">
                    <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-[#C5A26E] rounded-full animate-pulse"></div>
                    <span id="fate-signature-badge" class="text-[10px] tracking-[1.5px] text-[#C5A26E]/80 group-hover:text-[#C5A26E] transition">FATE ENGINE v4.3</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="hidden md:flex items-center gap-x-7 text-xs tracking-[2px]">
                <a href="#gundams" class="nav-link hover:text-[#C5A26E] transition">01 MOBILE SUITS</a>
                <a href="#factions" class="nav-link hover:text-[#C5A26E] transition">02 FACTIONS</a>
                <a href="#pilots" class="nav-link hover:text-[#C5A26E] transition">03 PILOTS</a>
                <a href="#gallery" class="nav-link hover:text-[#C5A26E] transition">04 FATE DANCE</a>
                
                <div class="w-px h-3 bg-white/20 mx-1"></div>
                
                <button onclick="showMyArchive()" 
                        class="flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1 text-xs tracking-[1.5px] border border-[#C5A26E]/50 hover:bg-[#C5A26E] hover:text-black rounded-full transition">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-heart text-[10px]"></i>
                    <span>MY ARCHIVE</span>
                </button>
                
                <button onclick="showRandomCinematicNote()" 
                        class="flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1 text-xs tracking-[1.5px] border border-white/20 hover:border-[#C5A26E] hover:text-[#C5A26E] rounded-full transition group">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-film text-[10px]"></i>
                    <span>INTERVENE</span>
                </button>
            </div>

            <!-- Mobile Hamburger -->
            <button onclick="showMobileNav()" class="md:hidden w-9 h-9 flex items-center justify-center text-lg text-white/70 hover:text-white">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-bars"></i>
            </button>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Hero - Cinematic Title Sequence -->
    <div class="relative h-screen flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden" 
         style="background-image: url('assets/gundam/strike-freedom-gundam.jpg'); background-size: cover; background-position: center 20%; background-repeat: no-repeat;">
        
        <!-- Multi-layer cinematic overlays -->
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-black/70 via-black/45 to-black/85"></div>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(#000_0.8px,transparent_1px)] bg-[length:3px_3px] opacity-40"></div>
        
        <!-- Subtle film breathing -->
        <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none" style="background: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 45%, rgba(197,162,110,0.04) 0%, transparent 70%); animation: heroBreath 8s ease-in-out infinite;"></div>
        
        <div class="relative z-10 text-center px-6 max-w-5xl">
            <div class="mb-6">
                <div class="inline-block px-5 py-1 text-[10px] tracking-[4px] border border-white/25 rounded-full text-white/60 mb-4">COSMIC ERA 71 — 73</div>
            </div>
            
            <h1 class="cinematic-title text-[92px] md:text-[120px] leading-[0.88] font-bold tracking-[-7.5px] mb-4 text-white">
                FREEDOM<br>
                <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#C5A26E] via-white to-[#C8102E] bg-clip-text text-transparent">IS A CHOICE</span>
            </h1>
            
            <p class="max-w-md mx-auto text-2xl text-white/70 tracking-tight mb-12">
                在命运的褶皱中，选择成为光。
            </p>
            
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
                <button onclick="document.getElementById('gundams').scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth' })" 
                        class="group px-14 py-4 bg-white text-black font-semibold tracking-[3px] text-sm rounded-2xl flex items-center gap-3 hover:bg-[#C5A26E] hover:text-black transition-all active:scale-[0.985]">
                    ENTER THE ARCHIVE
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-play text-xs group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition"></i>
                </button>
                <button onclick="showRandomCinematicNote()" 
                        class="px-8 py-4 border border-white/30 hover:bg-white/5 rounded-2xl text-sm tracking-[2.5px] transition flex items-center gap-2">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-film"></i>
                    <span>ASK THE ARCHIVIST</span>
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="absolute bottom-10 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 flex flex-col items-center text-[10px] tracking-[3px] text-white/40">
            <div>SCROLL TO BEGIN THE REEL</div>
            <div class="mt-1 w-px h-6 bg-white/20"></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Sequence 01: The Mobile Suits - Cinematic Reel -->
    <section id="gundams" class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 pt-16 pb-20">
        <!-- Cinematic Chapter Header -->
        <div class="mb-10">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
                <span class="text-xs tracking-[4px] text-[#C5A26E]/60">01</span>
                <div class="h-px w-12 bg-[#C5A26E]/40"></div>
                <span class="text-xs tracking-[3px] text-[#C5A26E]/60">THE STEEL WILL</span>
            </div>
