            <p class="max-w-xl text-lg text-white/70">二十台在命运褶皱中诞生的钢铁之诗。每一台，都是一个关于自由、正义与枷锁的章节。</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Unified Projector Controls - Clean cinematic Director's Lens (redesigned layout) -->
        <div class="mb-6">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3 px-1">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[#C5A26E]/70 text-xs tracking-[3px]">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-film"></i>
                    <span>DIRECTOR'S LENS</span>
                </div>
                <div class="text-[10px] text-white/40 tracking-widest hidden sm:block">SCROLL OR DRAG THE REEL • FATE GLOW = YOUR PROFILE</div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-[#111]/60 border border-white/10 rounded-3xl px-4 py-3 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center gap-3 md:gap-4">
                <!-- Search -->
                <div class="relative flex-1 min-w-[200px]">
                    <input id="gundam-search" type="text" placeholder="搜索机体、驾驶员、势力..." 
                           class="w-full bg-[#0A0A0A] border border-white/10 focus:border-[#C5A26E] text-sm rounded-2xl pl-10 py-2.5 placeholder:text-white/30 outline-none transition">
