                    <i class="fa-solid fa-heart text-[#C5A26E]"></i>
                    <span class="hidden sm:inline">MY ARCHIVE</span>
                    <span class="sm:hidden">收藏</span>
                    <span id="fav-count-badge" class="fav-count">0</span>
                </button>

                <!-- 命运抽选 - 诺兰式随机命运探索 -->
                <button onclick="surpriseMeGundam()" 
                        class="filter-chip px-4 py-2 text-xs tracking-widest border border-[#C8102E]/50 hover:bg-[#C8102E] hover:text-white hover:border-[#C8102E] rounded-2xl flex items-center gap-1.5 transition ml-1"
                        title="命运抽选 (或按 R 键) — 让随机决定你今天要研究的机动战士">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-dice"></i>
                    <span class="hidden sm:inline">命运抽选</span>
                    <span class="text-[9px] opacity-60 hidden lg:inline">R</span>
                </button>

                <!-- 排序 -->
                <select id="gundam-sort" class="filter-chip text-xs tracking-widest border border-white/15 bg-[#111] px-3 py-2 rounded-2xl ml-1 focus:border-[#C5A26E]">
                    <option value="default">默认顺序</option>
                    <option value="name">名称 A-Z</option>
                    <option value="pilot">驾驶员 A-Z</option>
                    <option value="model">型号</option>
                </select>

                <button onclick="clearGundamFilters()" 
                        class="filter-chip text-xs tracking-widest border border-white/15 hover:border-white/40 px-3 py-2 rounded-2xl ml-1 transition">
                    清除筛选
                </button>

                <!-- 实时结果计数 + 筛选状态 (档案馆专业感，可点击清除) -->
                <div id="gundam-results-count" 
                     class="text-xs text-white/50 ml-2 whitespace-nowrap cursor-pointer hover:text-[#C5A26E] transition flex items-center gap-1"
                     title="点击清除所有筛选"
                     aria-live="polite">
                    <span>显示 <span id="gundam-visible-count">20</span> / 20</span>
                    <span id="gundam-filter-summary" class="ml-1 text-[#C5A26E]/70 font-medium"></span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="film-reel" id="gundam-grid" role="list" aria-label="机动战士高达 钢铁意志胶片序列 — 横向放映卷轴，支持命运共振光影与拖拽浏览" data-sequence="01">
            <!-- 内容由 renderGundams() 动态生成 • 现在是 35mm 物理胶片卷轴 (Sequence 01) -->
            <!-- 每个 .gundam-card 成为独立 film frame，scroll-snap + fate 实时投射 -->
        </div>

        <!-- Diegetic projector frame counter HUD (live updated in reel init) -->
        <div id="reel-frame-hud" class="flex items-center justify-end gap-2 text-[10px] tracking-[3px] text-[#C5A26E]/70 font-medium mt-1.5 pr-1 select-none" aria-hidden="true">
            <span>SEQ 01 — STEEL WILL</span>
            <span class="text-[#C5A26E]/40">·</span>
            <span>FRAME <span id="reel-current-frame" class="tabular-nums text-[#C5A26E]">01</span> / <span id="reel-total-frames" class="tabular-nums">20</span></span>
        </div>

        <!-- Final note — suppressed for immersive reel (moved to archive footer in later cycle) -->
        <div class="mt-3 text-center hidden" aria-hidden="true">
            <div class="text-xs text-white/50">以上机体均为《机动战士高达SEED》及《SEED Destiny》官方登场MS · 所有设计、型号、驾驶员严格基于官方动画进行二次审查</div>
        </div>

        <!-- Projector control strip hint (Director's Lens) -->
        <div class="text-[9px] text-[#C5A26E]/50 tracking-[2px] mt-2 pl-1 flex items-center gap-2">
            <span>DRAG TO SCRUB • ←→ KEYS • FATE GLOW = PERSONAL RESONANCE</span>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 史诗对位：三国演义 × 诺兰史诗 × SEED (主题彩蛋) -->
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-8 py-12 border-t border-white/10">
        <div class="text-center mb-8">
            <div class="section-label tracking-[4px]">EPIC PARALLELS</div>
            <div class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight mt-1">三国演义 × 诺兰史诗 × 机动战士SEED</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-sm">
            <div class="bg-[#111] border border-white/10 rounded-3xl p-6">
                <div class="text-[#C5A26E] text-xs tracking-widest mb-2">基拉 · 大和</div>
                <div class="font-medium mb-2">如刘备之仁 / 如诺兰笔下“救世主”</div>
                <div class="text-white/70 leading-snug">从被迫卷入战争的少年，到最终选择守护“自由”的王者。背负着“天然协调者”的宿命，如同身处三国乱世却渴望结束乱世的仁君。</div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-[#111] border border-white/10 rounded-3xl p-6">
                <div class="text-[#C5A26E] text-xs tracking-widest mb-2">阿斯兰 · 萨拉</div>
                <div class="font-medium mb-2">如关羽之义 / 诺兰式“道德困境”</div>
                <div class="text-white/70 leading-snug">在父亲、祖国、友情、恋人之间反复撕裂。最终选择“正义”而非“复仇”，宛如关羽千里走单骑后的最终抉择。</div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-[#111] border border-white/10 rounded-3xl p-6">
                <div class="text-[#C5A26E] text-xs tracking-widest mb-2">真 · 飞鸟</div>
                <div class="font-medium mb-2">如吕布 / 张飞之烈 + 诺兰“时间”主题</div>
                <div class="text-white/70 leading-snug">被仇恨与命运反复折磨的少年。命运高达的每一次出击，都是诺兰电影里“时间褶皱”中不断重生的灵魂。</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center mt-6 text-[10px] text-white/40 tracking-[2px]">仅供爱好者脑内对位 · 致敬《三国演义》与诺兰式史诗张力</div>
    </div>

    <!-- Factions -->
    <section id="factions" class="border-y border-white/10 py-16 bg-[#0A0A0A]">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8">
            <div class="mb-10">
                <div class="section-label">FACTIONS</div>
                <h2 class="text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight">主要势力</h2>
            </div>

            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                <!-- ZAFT -->
                <div onclick="showFactionDetail('zaft')" class="group bg-[#111] rounded-3xl border border-white/10 overflow-hidden cursor-pointer hover:border-[#C5A26E] transition-all">
                    <img loading="lazy" src="assets/gundam/faction_zaft.jpg" class="w-full h-48 object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700" alt="ZAFT">
                    <div class="p-6">
                        <div class="text-[#C8102E] text-sm tracking-widest mb-2">ZAFT</div>
                        <div class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">扎夫特</div>
                        <div class="text-sm text-white/70">以协调者为中心建立的军事组织，基地位于PLANT太空殖民地。拥有最先进的MS技术，是SEED时代最主要的军事力量之一。</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Earth Alliance -->
                <div onclick="showFactionDetail('earth_alliance')" class="group bg-[#111] rounded-3xl border border-white/10 overflow-hidden cursor-pointer hover:border-[#C5A26E] transition-all">
                    <img loading="lazy" src="assets/gundam/faction_earth_alliance.jpg" class="w-full h-48 object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700" alt="Earth Alliance">
                    <div class="p-6">
                        <div class="text-[#0033A0] text-sm tracking-widest mb-2">EARTH ALLIANCE</div>
                        <div class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">地球联合军</div>
                        <div class="text-sm text-white/70">由大西洋联邦、欧亚联邦等国家组成的自然人军事联盟。开发了GAT-X系列MS，是对抗ZAFT的主要力量。</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Orb Union -->
                <div onclick="showFactionDetail('orb')" class="group bg-[#111] rounded-3xl border border-white/10 overflow-hidden cursor-pointer hover:border-[#C5A26E] transition-all">
                    <img loading="lazy" src="assets/gundam/faction_orb.jpg" class="w-full h-48 object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700" alt="Orb Union">
                    <div class="p-6">
                        <div class="text-[#C5A26E] text-sm tracking-widest mb-2">ORB UNION</div>
                        <div class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">奥布联合首长国</div>
                        <div class="text-sm text-white/70">中立国家，由雅兰·阿斯哈家族统治。以“永不参与战争”为国策，拥有世界顶尖的军事科技（M1 Astray等）。</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- PLANT -->
                <div onclick="showFactionDetail('plant')" class="group bg-[#111] rounded-3xl border border-white/10 overflow-hidden cursor-pointer hover:border-[#C5A26E] transition-all">
                    <img loading="lazy" src="assets/gundam/faction_plant.jpg" class="w-full h-48 object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700" alt="PLANT">
                    <div class="p-6">
                        <div class="text-red-400 text-sm tracking-widest mb-2">PLANT</div>
                        <div class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">太空殖民地</div>
                        <div class="text-sm text-white/70">协调者（Coordinator）建立的太空殖民地群，由最高评议会领导。ZAFT是其军事武装力量。</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Blue Cosmos / LOGOS -->
                <div onclick="showFactionDetail('blue_cosmos')" class="group bg-[#111] rounded-3xl border border-white/10 overflow-hidden cursor-pointer hover:border-[#C5A26E] transition-all">
                    <img loading="lazy" src="assets/gundam/faction_blue_cosmos.jpg" class="w-full h-48 object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700" alt="Blue Cosmos">
                    <div class="p-6">
                        <div class="text-blue-400 text-sm tracking-widest mb-2">BLUE COSMOS / LOGOS</div>
                        <div class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">反协调者组织</div>
                        <div class="text-sm text-white/70">极端反协调者（Naturals优先）恐怖组织。在SEED Destiny中演变为幕后黑手LOGOS，操纵战争。</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Terminal -->
                <div onclick="showFactionDetail('terminal')" class="group bg-[#111] rounded-3xl border border-white/10 overflow-hidden cursor-pointer hover:border-[#C5A26E] transition-all">
                    <img loading="lazy" src="assets/gundam/faction_terminal.jpg" class="w-full h-48 object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700" alt="Terminal">
                    <div class="p-6">
                        <div class="text-[#C5A26E] text-sm tracking-widest mb-2">TERMINAL</div>
                        <div class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">终端</div>
                        <div class="text-sm text-white/70">拉克丝·克莱因在SEED Destiny时期建立的秘密组织，致力于阻止战争扩大和暴露幕后黑手。</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Pilots & Characters • Sequence 02 -->
    <section id="pilots" class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 py-20">
        <div class="mb-6">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
                <div>
                    <div class="section-label">SEQUENCE 02 — CHARACTER REEL</div>
                    <h2 class="text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight">主要驾驶员与人物 <span class="text-sm align-super text-[#C5A26E]/60 tracking-[2px] font-normal">35MM FILM</span></h2>
                </div>
                <div class="hidden md:flex items-center text-[10px] text-[#C5A26E]/50 tracking-widest">DRAG • FATE RESONANCE ON PILOTS</div>
            </div>
            <!-- Light matching Projector hint + FATE DRAW for symmetry (Cycle 18 extension of (a)) -->
            <div class="text-[10px] text-[#C5A26E]/40 tracking-[1px] flex items-center gap-2">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-film"></i> 
                <span>THE HUMAN COST OF WAR — SCRUB TO FEEL THEIR STORIES</span>
                <button onclick="(function(){if(!window.fateProfile||!window.characters)return;const p=window.fateProfile;const chars=window.characters;let best=null,max=0;chars.forEach(c=>{let r=0;if(c.faction&&p.factionAffinity){const f=c.faction.split(/→|→|\/|\s+/)[0].trim();r+=(p.factionAffinity[f]||0)*1.5;}if(p.viewed&&p.viewed[c.id])r+=p.viewed[c.id].count*3;if(p.favoredPilots&&p.favoredPilots.some(pp=>c.name.includes(pp)))r+=8;if(r>max){max=r;best=c;}});if(best){const el=document.querySelector(`#character-grid .character-card[data-char-id='${best.id}']`);if(el){el.scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth',block:'center'});setTimeout(()=>{el.classList.add('fate-resonance');setTimeout(()=>el.classList.remove('fate-resonance'),1200);},300);}}})()" class="ml-2 px-2 py-0.5 text-[8px] tracking-widest border border-[#C5A26E]/40 hover:bg-[#C5A26E] hover:text-black rounded">FATE DRAW</button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="film-reel" id="character-grid" data-sequence="02" aria-label="人物胶片序列 — 横向命运卷轴，支持共振高光">
            <!-- Populated by renderCharacters() • 现在是物理胶片横向序列，与 Sequence 01 统一沉浸语言 -->
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Character Relationships -->
    <section id="relationships" class="border-y border-white/10 py-16 bg-[#0A0A0A]">
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-8">
            <div class="mb-10">
                <div class="section-label">RELATIONSHIPS</div>
                <h2 class="text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight">人物关系</h2>
            </div>
            
            <div class="space-y-6 text-lg">
                <!-- 个人恋爱关系 -->
                <div class="flex gap-8 items-center border-b border-white/10 pb-6">
                    <div class="w-40 text-[#C5A26E] font-medium">基拉 × 拉克丝</div>
                    <div class="text-white/80">从战场上的敌人到深爱彼此的伴侣。拉克丝是基拉心中的“歌姬”与精神支柱。</div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex gap-8 items-center border-b border-white/10 pb-6">
                    <div class="w-40 text-[#C5A26E] font-medium">阿斯兰 × 卡嘉莉</div>
                    <div class="text-white/80">青梅竹马的恋人。阿斯兰最终选择与卡嘉莉站在一起。</div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex gap-8 items-center border-b border-white/10 pb-6">
                    <div class="w-40 text-[#C5A26E] font-medium">真 × 露娜玛丽亚</div>
                    <div class="text-white/80">命运高达与命运的羁绊。露娜玛丽亚是真最坚定的支持者。</div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex gap-8 items-center border-b border-white/10 pb-6">
                    <div class="w-40 text-[#C5A26E] font-medium">阿斯兰 × 基拉</div>
                    <div class="text-white/80">曾经的挚友与对手。两人最终选择共同守护和平。</div>
                </div>

                <!-- 势力关系补充 -->
                <div class="flex gap-8 items-center border-b border-white/10 pb-6">
                    <div class="w-40 text-[#C5A26E] font-medium">ZAFT ↔ 地球联合</div>
                    <div class="text-white/80">SEED时代两大对立军事势力，协调者与自然人的战争核心。</div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex gap-8 items-center border-b border-white/10 pb-6">
                    <div class="w-40 text-[#C5A26E] font-medium">奥布 ↔ 双方</div>
                    <div class="text-white/80">中立国家，却多次被卷入战争，最终成为关键第三方力量。</div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex gap-8 items-center border-b border-white/10 pb-6">
                    <div class="w-40 text-[#C5A26E] font-medium">PLANT ↔ LOGOS</div>
                    <div class="text-white/80">SEED Destiny中，杜兰达尔领导的PLANT与幕后黑手LOGOS的暗中对抗。</div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex gap-8 items-center">
                    <div class="w-40 text-[#C5A26E] font-medium">终端（Lacus） ↔ 各方</div>
                    <div class="text-white/80">拉克丝的地下组织，致力于揭露真相、阻止战争扩大。</div>
                </div>
