    <!-- Cosmic Era Timeline — 诺兰式史诗时间线 -->
    <section class="border-y border-white/10 py-16 bg-[#0A0A0A]">
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-8">
            <div class="mb-10 text-center">
                <div class="section-label tracking-[4px]">COSMIC ERA CHRONICLES</div>
                <h2 class="text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight mt-1">命运的褶皱</h2>
                <p class="text-white/60 mt-3 max-w-md mx-auto">以诺兰式的非线性与宿命感重现 SEED 宇宙的关键时刻。每一刻都改变了无数人的轨迹。</p>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-8 relative before:absolute before:left-8 md:before:left-1/2 before:top-0 before:bottom-0 before:w-px before:bg-white/10" id="cosmic-timeline">
                <!-- Timeline Item 1 -->
                <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 md:gap-8 items-start">
                    <div class="md:w-1/2 md:text-right md:pr-8">
                        <div class="text-[#C5A26E] text-xs tracking-[3px]">C.E. 70</div>
                        <div class="text-2xl font-semibold">血染的开端</div>
                        <div class="text-sm text-white/70 mt-2">第一次世界大战爆发。ZAFT对地球联合军发动“血染的瓦伦泰”攻击。协调者与自然人的战争正式拉开帷幕。</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pl-8">
                        <div class="inline-block px-4 py-1 text-xs bg-white/5 rounded-full tracking-widest border border-white/10">THE INCITING INCIDENT</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Timeline Item 2 -->
                <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 md:gap-8 items-start">
                    <div class="md:w-1/2 md:text-right md:pr-8 md:order-1">
                        <div class="text-[#C5A26E] text-xs tracking-[3px]">C.E. 71 · HELIOPOLIS</div>
                        <div class="text-2xl font-semibold">GAT-X计划与基拉的觉醒</div>
                        <div class="text-sm text-white/70 mt-2">在废弃的殖民地，基拉·大和被迫驾驶 Strike Gundam 参战。从普通学生变成战场上的“天然协调者”。</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pl-8 md:order-2">
                        <div class="inline-block px-4 py-1 text-xs bg-[#C8102E]/10 text-[#C8102E] rounded-full tracking-widest border border-[#C8102E]/30">THE HERO'S CALL</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Timeline Item 3 -->
                <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 md:gap-8 items-start">
                    <div class="md:w-1/2 md:text-right md:pr-8">
                        <div class="text-[#C5A26E] text-xs tracking-[3px]">C.E. 71 · 雅弗兰</div>
                        <div class="text-2xl font-semibold">自由与正义的诞生</div>
                        <div class="text-sm text-white/70 mt-2">ZAFT第二阶段MS Freedom与Justice出击。基拉与阿斯兰在战场上重逢，友情与理念的第一次激烈碰撞。</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pl-8">
                        <div class="inline-block px-4 py-1 text-xs bg-white/5 rounded-full tracking-widest border border-white/10">THE DUEL OF FATES</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Timeline Item 4 -->
                <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 md:gap-8 items-start">
                    <div class="md:w-1/2 md:text-right md:pr-8 md:order-1">
                        <div class="text-[#C5A26E] text-xs tracking-[3px]">C.E. 73 · SEED DESTINY</div>
                        <div class="text-2xl font-semibold">命运的少年与复仇之翼</div>
                        <div class="text-sm text-white/70 mt-2">真·飞鸟驾驶Impulse Gundam登场。因战争失去一切的少年，怀着刻骨仇恨加入ZAFT。命运高达的引擎点燃了新的悲剧循环。</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pl-8 md:order-2">
                        <div class="inline-block px-4 py-1 text-xs bg-[#C8102E]/10 text-[#C8102E] rounded-full tracking-widest border border-[#C8102E]/30">THE NEW PROTAGONIST</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Timeline Item 5 -->
                <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 md:gap-8 items-start">
                    <div class="md:w-1/2 md:text-right md:pr-8">
                        <div class="text-[#C5A26E] text-xs tracking-[3px]">C.E. 73 · 拉格朗日点</div>
                        <div class="text-2xl font-semibold">命运计划与最终抉择</div>
                        <div class="text-sm text-white/70 mt-2">杜兰达尔主席发动“命运计划”，试图用基因决定人类未来。基拉、阿斯兰、拉克丝、卡嘉莉在月球上进行最终的理念对决。</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pl-8">
                        <div class="inline-block px-4 py-1 text-xs bg-white/5 rounded-full tracking-widest border border-white/10">THE PHILOSOPHICAL CLIMAX</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Timeline Item 6 -->
                <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 md:gap-8 items-start">
                    <div class="md:w-1/2 md:text-right md:pr-8 md:order-1">
                        <div class="text-[#C5A26E] text-xs tracking-[3px]">C.E. 73 · 终章</div>
                        <div class="text-2xl font-semibold">光翼下的和平</div>
                        <div class="text-sm text-white/70 mt-2">强袭自由与无限正义并肩作战，击碎命运的枷锁。战后，基拉与拉克丝隐居小岛。战争结束了，但“选择”的重量永远留在了每个人心中。</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pl-8 md:order-2">
                        <div class="inline-block px-4 py-1 text-xs bg-emerald-900/30 text-emerald-400 rounded-full tracking-widest border border-emerald-400/30">THE QUIET AFTERMATH</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="text-center mt-10 text-xs text-white/40">“时间不是线性的，而是被选择不断折叠的。” — 致敬 Christopher Nolan 的叙事哲学</div>
            <div class="text-center mt-2 text-[10px] text-white/30">点击时间线事件可跳转查看相关高达档案</div>
        </div>
    </section>

